{"tid":2236409,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"宣道小學教師因討論言論自由被釘牌，教協和本土派沒有告訴你的是……","createTime":"2020-10-09T12:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T10:54:08.000Z","uid":276028,"like":4,"dislike":107,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b67acc013da08be8787dcc2ef53603eeda8c1499","tid":2236409,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"原來，宣道小學老師被釘牌，教協和本土派沒有告訴你的真相是，他們追求民主運動的終點或許只是恢復港英舊貌，是非追求廣大民眾的生活改善？<br />\n宣道小學的老師是業界的清泉，有部分老師的教學十分不堪？<br />\n如何不堪？<br />\n宣道小學的老師和一般人之患相比，教學方法有何不同？<br />\n教協沒有以教學願景團結公眾向政府施壓推行實際改革，所謂何事？<br />\n<br />\n/但是，仍然有不少教師（含教協會員）只是抱著打份工的心態，沒有像宣道小學的老師這樣，願意製作有思考性的問題工作紙，並接受學生有創意合理的答案。不少教師（不如稱為人之患）只是上課時依書而讀，改功課時只用標準答案定奪學生的生死和分數的高低，扼殺學生的好奇心和創意力。/<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.boyangu.com/sc/education/hkptu-alliance-2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boyangu.com%2Fsc%2Feducation%2Fhkptu-alliance-2020%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYznqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=64111bb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.boyangu.com/sc/education/hkptu-alliance-2020/</a>"},{"pid":"6bb14905aac058dcabe28b395b43245158aeed29","tid":2236409,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:32:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26ba0f6407394c122db08fd8e81166065cfa1711","tid":2236409,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:58:17.000Z","msg":"自推。"},{"pid":"203d3c942904bf62b3f63b6f7d2a3dc531a73880","tid":2236409,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:44:06.000Z","msg":"自推。"},{"pid":"ece1714a30e3e9450581dfdcb3cc2b5648c12618","tid":2236409,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:06:17.000Z","msg":"自推。"},{"pid":"a0c498c8a6615c2d5f21865cc6ada8b52c1805c8","tid":2236409,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T16:16:58.000Z","msg":"自推。"},{"pid":"3af8c68b752dbe446e89e6161ea0dc06261c5eee","tid":2236409,"uid"